Of course plans can change. We don‚Äôt know how long group projects will take and the timeframe might change as we go along. The nice thing about this course is that we have ultimate flexibility; we can push deadlines back if we need more time than we thought.
At this stage workshops and Q&A sessions will run in person but we may have to switch to online only at any moment. Either way, the workshops will streamed on zoom for those who are unable to make it to class.
There are two reasons not to come to class.
if you are overseas and studying remotely
if attending class in person would pose a health risk to everyone
if you have been identified as a contact of someone with COVID
OR if you have the slightest sniffle, please don‚Äôt come (go get a test instead).
Let us know and we will make sure you don‚Äôt miss out on the content.
